sequenceDiagram
  participant App as Lab script / future API
  participant Redis as Redis :6379
  participant Source as JSON file or DB

  App->>Redis: GET cxr:claim:analyzed:{id}
  alt cache miss
    Redis-->>App: (nil)
    App->>Source: load artifact
    Source-->>App: claim JSON
    App->>Redis: SETEX key TTL payload
  else cache hit
    Redis-->>App: cached JSON
  end
  Note over App,Redis: Invalidate on write: DEL key
